  "detailed_description": "<h1>加入社群</h1><p>QQ群：904149766<br>B站：左安门少侠</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/a6d85460daadb1bf467587e77fe86a70.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/d6ea9320b4fc5c9df003f7c870e3fef2.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/d6ea9320b4fc5c9df003f7c870e3fef2.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/d6ea9320b4fc5c9df003f7c870e3fef2.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>先敌预判、见招拆招、锁定弱点、一击制胜！用智慧击败强敌！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/b68af34ce49e6184b47167c6d09f60e6.avif?t=1721726222\" width=554 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/13bb44b93c2e69e832b8d5079fad3f1c.poster.avif?t=1721726222\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/13bb44b93c2e69e832b8d5079fad3f1c.webm?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082620/extras/13bb44b93c2e69e832b8d5079fad3f1c.mp4?t=1721726222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>搭配几十种兵刃、饰品和招式，定义属于你自己的战斗风格！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_